Morningside Drive (stop the slope, buildings thereupon), at West
121st Street as viewed westward from Morningside Park and showing
several apartment houses that are from left to right, the 6 story
Palemetto, the 9 Story Janus Court, the 6 story Shelbourne Hall, the 5 [sic] story Circle and the 6 story Curty Rebelle.
April 1915.
George L. Balgue.

Another view of the same area from a point slightly to the south.
April 1915
George L. Balgue.

Note May, 21, 2015:
These are:
100 Morningside Drive
106 Morningside Drive (now called Seth Low Hall)
110 Morningside Drive
114 Morningside Drive (The Circle -- a 6 story building not 5)
130 Morningside Drive (now called Marie Runyon Hall)
